ot;</span></p><p class="c2"><span class="c4">At </span><span class="c5"><a class="c6" href="hxxps://storage[.]googleapis[.]com/lithesome/reachflow[.]html#index[.]php?search=4&d74468&jayye=226-32&lm=195982IREG2079&sd=8&page=tvuQuTw4otc4g2w">minute 3:07 of this leaked video</a></span><span class="c0">, you&#39;ll see EXACTLY how they ALL did it.</span></p><p class="c2"><span class="c0">That&#39;s when you&#39;ll realize the &quot;random&quot; lottery is the biggest lie ever told.</span></p><p class="c2"><span class="c4">&#128073; </span><span class="c5"><a class="c6" href="hxxps://storage[.]googleapis[.]com/lithesome/reachflow[.]html#index[.]php?search=4&d74468&awgfr=226-32&lm=195982QOYT2079&sd=8&page=WtcanYVzzTT7oQO">Watch Before They Shut This Down</a></span></p><p class="c2"><span class="c0">&#9888;&#65039; Warning: Already banned in Massachusetts. This loophole could be wiped out in your state next.</span></p><p class="c3"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 400.00px; height: 300.00px;"><img border="0"  alt="" src="hxxps://i[.]imgur[.]com/4g2KVvo[.]png" style="width: 400.00px; height: 300.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p></body></center>

